# Nola Touch environment variables
#
# This project currently requires NO environment variables to build or run.
# It is fully static and has no external service dependencies.
#
# When you add integrations later (payments, CMS, analytics, etc.), list the
# variables here (without real values) and configure the real values in the
# Vercel dashboard under Project Settings > Environment Variables.
#
# Example:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://nolatouch.com
